<div style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center; color: #333;">
  <h2>You are going to {{ eventTitle }}!</h2>
  <p>Your payment was successful. Please present the QR code below at the venue entrance.</p>
  
  <img src="cid:qrcode" alt="Ticket QR Code" style="width: 250px; height: 250px; border-radius: 10px; border: 2px solid #ddd; padding: 10px;" />
  
  <p style="margin-top: 20px; font-size: 12px; color: #777;">
    Do not share this QR code with anyone else. It can only be scanned once.
  </p>
</div>